%% Story2Belief — sequence view of the prototype run
%% See docs/02-prototype-roadmap-3mo.md

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Cfg as configs/prototype.yaml
    participant Pipe as Layer 1: Narrative pipeline
    participant Cohort as Layer 2: Reader cohort
    participant Bridge as Layer 3: Moral-transfer bridge
    participant Out as data/processed/

    Cfg ->> Pipe: corpus paths + prompt versions
    Pipe ->> Out: NarrativeFeatures (per text)
    Cfg ->> Cohort: trait sampling ranges + N
    Cohort ->> Out: ReaderProfile (per agent)
    Out ->> Cohort: NarrativeFeatures
    Cohort ->> Out: ReadingResponse (per agent x text)
    Out ->> Bridge: NarrativeFeatures + ReadingResponse + dilemma corpus
    Bridge ->> Out: TransferDeltas (per agent x text)
